thread.title: BRIEF-JRjr33 Will Not Meet Feb 15 Extension For Filing 10-Q

title: BRIEF-JRjr33 Will Not Meet Feb 15 Extension For Filing 10-Q
text: February 16, 2018 / 11:35 AM / in 16 minutes BRIEF-JRjr33 Will Not Meet Feb 15 Extension For Filing 10-Q Reuters Staff 1 Min Read Feb 16 (Reuters) - JRjr33 Inc: * JRJR33 INC SAYS ON FEB 15, CO SAID WILL NOT MEET FEB 15, 2018 EXTENSION GRANTED BY NYSE AMERICAN FOR FILING WITH SEC ITS FORMS 10-Q - SEC FILING * JRJR33 -ON FEB 15, CO SAID WILL NOT MEET FEB 15, 2018 EXTENSION, FOR FILING 10-Q, FOR PERIODS ENDED MARCH 31, 2017, JUNE 30, 2017 AND SEPT 30, 2017 * JRJR33 - CO ATTRIBUTES THE DELAY PRIMARILY TO THE BALANCING OF CERTAIN NON-CASH INTRA-DIVISIONAL CHARGES Source text: ( bit.ly/2CnZOBX ) Further company coverage:
